laboratory_examinations.findings: The CT showed a heterogeneous collection in the right upper quadrant adjacent to the second portion of the duodenum measuring 6.9 x 4 x 6.6 cm, with small focus of air. There has been progressive worsening and increasing organization of the fluid collection since prior.
